# 📊 Student Performance Dashboard (Tableau)

## 📌 Overview

This project presents an interactive Tableau dashboard analyzing student performance across key academic indicators, including GPA, attendance, and course-level performance.

The dashboard is designed to provide clear insights into trends, relationships, and variations in student outcomes.

---

## 🎯 Key Features

* KPI summary of overall performance (Average Attendance, GPA, Total Students, Risk Students)
* Semester-wise GPA trends
* Course-wise performance comparison
* Relationship between attendance and GPA (scatter plot)
* Distribution of GPA across students

---

## 🔍 Key Insights

* GPA remains relatively stable across semesters
* Performance varies slightly across different courses
* Higher attendance is associated with higher GPA
* Student performance shows noticeable variation across individuals

---

## 🛠 Tools Used

* Tableau
* Data Visualization
* Data Analysis

